OL,3,CMan charged over murder in Portadown
OL,5,FA man has been charged to court with
OL,6,Fthe murder of a man in Portadown.
OL,8,FRolandas Kvederis, 49, was pronounced
OL,9,Fdead at the scene after emergency
OL,10,Fservices attended a property in
OL,11,FRanfurley Road on Thursday night.
OL,13,FPolice had received a report of an
OL,14,Faltercation at the property shortly
OL,15,Fafter 11pm on Thursday. Mr Kvederis
OL,16,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,18,FThe man in his 50s is due to appear
OL,19,Fbefore Lisburn Magistrates' court on
OL,20,FMonday.
